Package: libsafe-shm-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libfmt-dev
Description: Lock-free shared memory primitives - development files
 Header-only C++23 library providing seqlock, cyclic ring buffer,
 time-series temporal queries, and lifecycle management over POSIX
 shared memory. Uses per-slot seqlocks, Linux futex, and std::atomic_ref.
 .
 This package contains the header files for development.
